  "reasons": [
    {
      "category": "other",
      "description": [
        {
          "value": "近年来频繁采取干涉中国内政、损害中方利益的言行，并于近期率团窜访中国台湾地区，严重违反一个中国原则和中美三个联合公报规定，严重损害中国主权和领土完整，向\"台独\"分裂势力发出严重错误信号。",
          "lang": "zh",
          "script": "Hani",
          "is_primary": true
        },
        {
          "value": "Frequently engaged in actions interfering in China's internal affairs and harming China's interests, and recently led a delegation to visit China's Taiwan region, seriously violating the One-China principle and the three China-US joint communiqués, seriously damaging China's sovereignty and territorial integrity, and sending seriously wrong signals to \"Taiwan independence\" separatist forces.",
          "lang": "en",
          "script": "Latn",
          "is_primary": false
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
